sentences.english: With its advantageous resource combination, tourism can be a leading industry in Kuche's development of economy.
sentences.chinese: 旅游业可以成为库车经济发展的主导产业。

sentences.english: Kucha (Kuche) city downtown of Xinjiang China.
sentences.chinese: 中国新疆库车市的市景。

sentences.english: In the eastern Kuche Depression, Mesozoic Cretaceous and Cenozoic Tertiary are the main depositis.
sentences.chinese: 库车坳陷东部中新生代地层主要发育白垩系和第三系。

sentences.english: Kuche Depression, a foreland depression, is situated in the northen Tarim Basin.
sentences.chinese: 库车坳陷位于塔里木盆地北部，为一前陆坳陷。

sentences.english: It can also accept continental hydrocarbon lateral migration southward from the Kuche Depression on the north.
sentences.chinese: 它也能接受北面库车坳陷向南侧向运移的陆相油气。

sentences.english: Kuche apricot meat meat is not only strong, sweet and sour taste, even it is sweet.
sentences.chinese: 库车杏不仅肉厚味浓，酸甜适口，连杏核也是甜的。

sentences.english: There are two overpressure systems, lower and upper overpressure systems, in Kuqa foreland basin.
sentences.chinese: 库车前陆盆地具有典型的双超压体系。

sentences.english: The Kelasu tectonic zone located in the Kuqa Depression of the Tarim Basin is rich in natural gas.
sentences.chinese: 克拉苏构造带是库车坳陷天然气最富集的区带之一。

sentences.english: But Kuche not beautiful girls, beautiful to have the field instead.
sentences.chinese: 但是这库车的女孩却不漂亮，漂亮的都到外地去了吧。
